series.name: Spartacus: House of Ashur
series.overview: In a world where he survived the events of Spartacus (2010), Ashur clawed his way to power, owning the same ludus that once owned him. Allying with a fierce gladiatrix, Ashur ignites a new kind of spectacle that offends the elite.

series.name: The Abandons
series.overview: In 1850s Washington, two families led by powerful matriarchs — one wealthy, one poor but deeply loyal — battle for supremacy on the lawless frontier.

series.name: Heated Rivalry
series.overview: Two of the biggest stars in Major League Hockey are bound by ambition, rivalry, and a magnetic pull neither of them fully understands. What begins as a secret fling between two fresh faced rookies evolves into a years-long journey of love, denial, and self-discovery. Over the next eight years, as they chase glory on the ice, they struggle to navigate their feelings for each other. Torn between the sport they live for and the love they can’t ignore, they must decide if there’s room in their fiercely competitive world for something as fragile – and powerful – as real love.

series.name: The Price of Confession
series.overview: Accused of killing her husband, a woman is offered a way out by a mysterious stranger: in exchange for a confession in her place, she must commit murder.

series.name: Silence
series.overview: In the shadows of history, the secret beats like a pulse. Vampire sisters survive the shortage of 'clean human blood' caused by the Black Death, but the true poison is the silence that surrounds them. Centuries later, one of their descendants faces the same conflict during the AIDS pandemic in Spain, and discovers that the social condemnation remains the same. And that the love between 'sick' and 'healthy,' humans and vampires, continues to provoke the same terror. What happens when eternity is measured in centuries of silence?

series.name: Sean Combs: The Reckoning
series.overview: This documentary series unpacks the shocking allegations behind Sean "Diddy" Combs and his Bad Boy empire, spanning decades of his life and career.

series.name: Legend of the Magnate
series.overview: A wrongfully accused scholar, Gu Pingyuan, becomes a fugitive and uses his intelligence to build a commercial empire. Starting as a merchant, he establishes himself in various industries, clashes with different merchant groups, and ultimately aims to save the nation's economy, showcasing a generation of merchants who served their country through commerce.

series.name: Sandokan
series.overview: Sandokan is a Malaysian pirate who, along with his friend Yanez and their crew, attacks the British forces from his island of Mompracem. During his adventures, he falls in love with Lady Marianna Guillonk, an English-Italian aristocrat.

series.name: Love on the Turquoise Land
series.overview: It tells the story of a secret organization of supernatural abilities called "Nanshan Hunters." It follows Nie Jiuluo and Yan Tuo, which initially their relationship starts off combative, but after several life-and-death collaborations, they gradually develop mutual trust and affection. Together, they confront the villain Di Xiao, protect love and peace, and ultimately become life partners.

series.name: The Princess Decree
series.overview: When a political marriage ignites a long-awaited revenge, the returning Princess Royal and her former lover clash in the court’s power struggles. But as love and rivalry collide, they realize they are each other’s only salvation and join forces to reshape the kingdom’s future.

series.name: Surely Tomorrow
series.overview: In their twenties, Lee Kyeong-do and Seo Ji-woo part ways after two passionate relationships. A decade later, they meet again as a reporter who covers an adultery scandal and the wife of the man at the center of that scandal. Reuniting in their late thirties, their youth has passed, but their love remains vivid. Kyeong-do now strives to prove to her and to himself that he still loves her.

series.name: Sniper Butterfly
series.overview: A captivating romance unfolds between a confident, cat-like woman and a bold, loyal younger man. As they navigate their differences, they find mutual healing and redemption, leading to a passionate, fate-driven love story full of tension and desire.

series.name: Seher Hone Ko Hai
series.overview: Strong-willed Kausar defies societal barriers for her daughter Seher’s big dreams, but will destiny stand by their side?

series.name: Pro Bono
series.overview: When a respected judge's world falls apart overnight, he joins a top law firm's pro bono team — where hope and purpose wait in humble, unexpected places.

series.name: Realm's Night Rain Dreamlike
series.overview: Once a feared outlaw leader, Jiang Hu seeks a quiet life after a tragic failure leads to a loyal general’s downfall. But a run-in with a ruthless enemy pulls him back into danger. Joined by an old ally and a rescued orphan girl, he sets out to uncover the truth and fight for justice in a corrupt martial world.

series.name: Second Chance Romance
series.overview: Retired ballet artist Tan Siting returns to China, wanting to seek a second chance with Feng Rui, the lover she was once forced to leave behind. But past misunderstandings have built a wall between them. Feng Rui's orderly life as a a single father is thrown into chaos by her reappearance. Meanwhile, Tan Siting is accompanied by a man who has loved her from afar for a decade. As Tan Siting and Feng Rui try to avoid each other, fate keeps forcing them together, leaving them trapped in a turbulent mix of love and heartache.

series.name: Ripple
series.overview: In New York City, four strangers navigate life's challenges while their separate paths unexpectedly intertwine in ways that change them forever.

series.name: Treasure at Dawn
series.overview: Hua Fusheng is a young man who's innocent and obsessed with medicine. He uses unconventional methods that both endear and frighten the townspeople. He is wrongly accused of murder after the death of Bai Yi. Clues left behind by his mentor seem to point to a mysterious "Sacred Book." At the same time, Wen Jue, the daughter of Liangzhou city lord, and Gu Tian, an inheritor of the performing arts, get drawn into the mystery. The three of them head to Liangzhou to investigate. Wen Jue uses her family's influence to help Hua Fusheng open a clinic, while Gu Tian's quick wit aids them in gathering intel. As Hua Fusheng heals the poor, he hunts for the truth, but strange events unfold, and the puzzle deepens. Unknown to him, his arrival has already stirred hidden forces in Liangzhou...

series.name: All Rise
series.overview: A group of law interns compete in a high-stakes "top offer" challenge, where the fierce competition forces them to navigate intense workplace dynamics. Along the way, each of them discovers an opportunity that could change their lives and ignite their passions.

series.name: The War Between the Land and the Sea
series.original_name: The War Between the Land and the Sea
series.overview: When a fearsome and ancient species emerges from the ocean, dramatically revealing themselves to humanity, an international crisis is triggered. With the entire population at risk, UNIT step into action as the land and sea wage war.

series.name: Terra Alta
series.overview: It centred on the murder of two prominent businesspeople in Catalonia.

series.name: Fugue State 1986
series.overview: León and Jeremías' friendship, bonded by literature, shatters when one of them commits an unforgivable act of violence in Bogotá.

series.name: Reloved
series.original_name: เริ่มใหม่หัวใจเดิม
series.overview: A single dad balancing new fatherhood crosses paths with his long-lost ex, reigniting old feelings and uncovering the truth behind their broken past.

series.name: I Am Boxer
series.overview:
A legitimate bout will take place on the ring where the nation's best boxers have gathered!

Here comes a mega boxing survival, developed by Don Lee, a world-class action star and owner of a boxing gym with 30 years of boxing experience. Participants with diverse backgrounds, including medalists and even champions, gather for a fierce face-off and strive to reach the top. Who will overcome their limits, prove their potential, and rise as the champion? A gripping action show with striking sets, spectacular matches, and missions of incredible scale.

The world of authentic boxing, a mega blockbuster boxing survival that no one has ever experienced.

series.name: Sicily Express
series.overview: With Christmas around the corner, two blundering Sicilian friends working in Milan discover a dumpster that transports them to their families in seconds.

series.name: Burnout Syndrome
series.original_name: ภาวะรักคนหมดไฟ
series.overview: After losing his dream job, a burned-out artist falls between two men—a charming IT guy and a reclusive tycoon who hires him to be his public face.

series.name: The Palace Gambit
series.overview: Two sisters enter the palace and quickly earn the emperor’s favor, but their rise ends in tragedy when the elder sister—pregnant with the heir—is killed in a palace scheme. Left with nothing, the younger sister Lu Jiuning hides her grief and, as a lowly palace maid, carefully plots her revenge. Moving between rival consorts and imperial power, she wages a quiet but ruthless battle to avenge her sister’s death.

series.name: Thundercloud Rainstorm
series.overview: Bound by a debt, an illegitimate son moves in with his aloof cousin, unaware that their uneasy deal will spiral into a deep and dangerous obsession.

series.name: Love Is Blind: Italy
series.overview: A group of singles who want to be loved for who they are will have the opportunity to search for their soulmate without the distractions of the outside world and will choose someone to marry without ever meeting them face-to-face. When their wedding day arrives, will real-world realities and external factors push them apart, or will they marry the person they fell blindly in love with?

series.name: Twelve Dates 'Til Christmas
series.overview: Follows Saville Row textile pattern designer Kate, who lives in the quaint village of Blexford, England next door to her father Mac, who is long-divorced from Kate’s mother Delilah, a globe-trotting American always on an adventure.  When not at work, Kate looks after Mac, who’s recovering from a motorbike accident and is inclined to spend his days sitting in his recliner.  Her best friend Laura signs her up for The 12 Dates of Christmas – a holiday-themed matchmaking program in the days leading up to the holiday featuring carefully curated, yuletide dating experiences, in an attempt to get Kate out of her rut.

series.name: Back to the Origin
series.overview: Former financial anchor Zhang Ran, dissatisfied with an ordinary life abroad, returns to China with her husband Fu Yudong to pursue a career as a comedy influencer. Unexpectedly, her handyman husband, with a PhD, becomes the mascot CEO of a startup before she can find success. As they both navigate their own comedic and chaotic paths, the couple faces challenges, grows individually, and ultimately rediscovers love and purpose.

series.name: Melody of Secrets
series.original_name: ความลับในบทเพลงที่บรรเลงไม่รู้จบ
series.overview: An amnesiac journalist and a criminologist must work together to solve a string of brutal murders, slowly uncovering dangerous secrets in their past.

series.name: Kuttram Purindhavan
series.overview: In a small-town, when a girl goes missing, Retiree Baskaran takes extreme measures to protect his grandson, Esther is consumed by guilt, and powerless constable Gautham races to find the truth. Secrets surface, leading to an uneasy alliance between Baskaran and Gautham, to a final showdown, justice is served, but guilt leaves some with closure and others haunted.

series.name: Bound by Fate
series.overview: Ateş, a man haunted by childhood scars and consumed by rage, returns to destroy the family that shattered his life years ago. His weapon is not a sword, but a marriage: 187 days with Mercan, the daughter of his enemy. Mercan, already promised to Nezir, is thrust into a battle she never chose, while Ateş binds her to him believing she is the key to his revenge. Yet the woman he intends to destroy becomes the one who threatens to undo him. And in the shadows, Aslı – driven by jealousy, seizes every chance to tear them apart.

series.name: Three Idiots in Kenya
series.overview: Once a far-off promise, now a reality — three buddies finally hit the road in Kenya. Get ready for adventure, banter and maybe even a giraffe selfie.

series.name: The Nowhere Man
series.overview: Lukas, a former mercenary haunted by PTSD, roams the city as a waste picker with his trolley. At the homeless shelter where he lives, he salvages scraps to help others. Using his metalworking skill, he crafts statues and sells them to raise funds, quietly battling the violent past he longs to escape.

series.name: Aukaat Ke Bahar
series.overview: A small-town boxer enters an elite Delhi college to fulfill his brother's dream. He faces bullying and class discrimination while falling for an ambitious senior student, forcing him to fight for love and dignity.

series.name: Strange Chronicles of Tang: The Chang'an Detective
series.overview: Newly arrived constable Wei Tao is thrust into a baffling poison case when eight elders from a local charity die under mysterious circumstances. His investigation leads him to widow-physician Jiao Yu, where buried secrets and deadly traps begin to surface.

series.name: Baddies USA
series.overview:
Baddies USA kicks off in DC with a reunion of OG

Bad Girls and a Ballroom Dinner.

series.name: The Artist
series.overview: In the Gilded Age, an ensemble of the era’s celebrities including Thomas Edison, Edgar Degas and Evelyn Nesbit meet at the home of an eccentric and failing tycoon. By the end of the night, the mogul is found dead, spurring a historical fiction-themed murder mystery.

series.name: Match Play
series.overview: Stuntman Jae-Yeon starts teaching action scenes to idol Doh-ha, who comes to learn the moves, and the two start to grow closer. Even as they clash, they can’t help but grow curious about each other.

series.name: Sarcastic Family
series.overview: Emotionless Andromedan mother-daughter Cai Xiaoying and Li Lili, who parted ways on Earth, are forced to reconnect when Li marries human Meng for an interstellar survey. Cai, broke and demanding room and board, joins them, forming a snarky family with Meng’s ditzy dad, navigating hilarity and trials.

series.name: Shadow Detective
series.overview: In 1930s Shanghai, detective Guan Cen and university student Lu Yizhen, meet during an investigation into a mysterious death at a women’s dormitory. Two years later, Lu Yizhen becomes one of Shanghai’s first female police officers, working directly under Guan Cen. Together, they reopen an unresolved child kidnapping case, uncovering hidden truths and confronting the shadows of the past.

series.name: Extraordinary
series.overview: Shi Xiaofan, a modern engineer, transmigrates into a fictional dynasty as Shi Feifan, a notorious playboy, and secretly uses his advanced knowledge to protect his family, build power, and reshape the empire. While pretending to be irresponsible, he quietly amasses wealth, outsmarts political enemies, and rises from “good-for-nothing” to a hidden military force pivotal to the kingdom’s survival.

series.name: The Gate Of Mystical Realm
series.overview: In a world where warriors are respected, Shi Mu's fate seems destined to be unique. As a adopted son of aristocratic families, he was forced to embark on the path of a warrior who searched for the truth and self-salvation. From the competition between the four museums of Fengcheng to the battle between sects, interests are involved and strong enemies are surrounded by them. Every challenge makes Shi Mu more determined. In the end, Shi Mu realized his bloodline power, which not only changed his destiny, but also affected the future of many people.

series.name: Dreamy
series.overview: While working as a hairdresser in an Istanbul suburb, Aydan finds herself the owner of a luxury beauty salon. Her shadowy new boss is Emir, a mysterious businessman about whom no one knows anything. As Aydan struggles to adapt to Emir's world, she's also forced to contend with the troubles caused by her reluctant partner, Çiğdem, a vagrant who grew up in an orphanage. Efe, the reckless police officer who follows Emir, inevitably crosses paths with Çiğdem and the hairdresser. Amidst all this chaos, Aydan seeks solace in her dear friend, manicurist Fiko, while her ex-husband, talented hairdresser Tarık, who can't stomach Aydan's new world of luxury, finds himself facing a new problem every day.

series.name: Reborn from the Ashes
series.overview: After being reborn as Su Qingran, a noblewoman betrayed and killed in her past life returns to seek justice for herself and her family. Fate brings her into a political marriage with Wanyan Jin, a man burdened by his own deep-seated vendetta. Though initially wary of each other, they join forces to uncover the truth, avenge their families, and find love as they fight side by side.

series.name: Help! I got Married to My Mortal Enemy!
series.original_name: 救命，我怎么和死对头领证啦
series.overview: 25-year-old jewelry designer Deng Qianqian and her rival Zhou Yu had a drunken relationship by accident. They were bumped into by their parents and forced to get married. The two had a feud for twenty years because she accidentally killed his bird when she was six years old. Deng Qianqian hid in a resort hotel to escape from marriage. Little did she know that Zhou Yu had been secretly in love with her for many years, and it was inevitable to pursue his wife in a sinister manner. Deng Qianqian, whose card was frozen, was forced to serve Zhou Yu personally in exchange for money. Zhou Yu's preference gradually melted her prejudices. After the marriage, she encounters a wild boar while camping. Her love rival Shang Yulin's self-protection and Zhou Yu's sacrifice to protect each other completely unlock the crux of the matter. From tit-for-tat to affectionate confessions, the two finally held a wedding with everyone's blessings and gained a perfect love.

series.name: The Sparrow's Gambit
series.overview: After being betrayed by her adoptive father, the formidable and beautiful assassin Qingmao is left for dead. In her final moments, she uncovers the truth that the mastermind behind her family's annihilation has been lurking nearby. Burning with vengeance, she bides her time for five years, reinventing herself as the enchanting songstress Liu Rumeng. Now, under this new identity, she sets her revenge plan in motion...

series.name: Beauty Reborn
series.original_name: แผนรักฉบับร้าย
series.overview: Fresh out of college, ambitious cosmetic scientist Sara battles family struggles, office politics and a love triangle while saving a failing beauty firm.

series.name: Roja
series.overview: As a hostage crisis unfolds at his parents' resort, Liam must team up with his friend-turned-enemy and put aside old grudges to protect their loved ones.

series.name: Tidstjuven
series.overview: Ever since Clint's father Pontus disappeared on Christmas Eve five years ago, Clint has loathed Christmas. But everything changes when a mysterious man appears in his closet and drops a time spy. When Clint tries the binoculars, he sees his father stuck in ancient times. At the same time, strange things begin to happen - Gustav Vasa steps out of the closet, misplaced by 500 years. With the help of the time viewer, Clint embarks on a breathtaking adventure to save his father, where he travels through history.

series.name: Two Coffees
series.overview: Yahya El-Wakeel, a well-known writer and media figure in his mid-thirties, comes from a wealthy Upper Egyptian family with a blend of modern thought and deep-rooted Egyptian values and traditions. He falls in love with Nelly Naseem, an aristocratic woman who owns a classy café in Zamalek. Over time, fundamental differences in their worldviews begin to surface.

series.name: Ekaki
series.overview: A group of friends plan a fun weekend getaway to the mysterious Ekaki Villa, only to find themselves caught between laughter and fear when strange haunting begin. Filled with hilarious chaos, spooky twists, and emotional moments

series.name: Manslaughter Memory
series.overview: Su Ruan and Xu Zhongwen remain loyal to each other amid danger and deceit, standing firm against those with ill intentions. As they battle evil and uncover the truth, they learn to confront their pasts, let go of hatred, and courageously step into a new life together.

series.name: Marry Him in Her Place
series.overview: On her wedding night, wealthy heiress Liang Yi is betrayed by her husband, disfigured, and cast into a river. Rescued and given a new face, she assumes the identity of courtesan Xu Yin and draws close to gang leader Lin Yun, determined to take her revenge.

series.name: The Cross-Dressed Union
series.overview: Amid political chaos caused by the former emperor’s suppression of the military, the general’s son Nan Chenxiao disguises himself as a woman to stay safe, while aspiring official Rui Yu hides her identity by posing as a man. Forced into partnership through an unexpected marriage by the new emperor, the two face dangerous trials and uncover each other’s secrets to help the emperor restore stability to the realm.

series.name: Ziddi Ishq
series.overview: Mehul, a young woman whose innocent crush on her tuition teacher, Shekhar Da, develops into a dangerous obsession. After his death is ruled a suicide, Mehul refuses to accept the official story and begins her own investigation, which leads her to uncover a tangled web of secrets and lies.

series.name: The Disappeared of Compostela
series.overview: Jeanne Nogarède is a police officer in her home village of Saint-Guilhem-le-Désert. The biggest regret of her life: the case of Emma Vivian, the daughter of one of her childhood friends, who disappeared on her way to school. Five years later, a new element shakes up her understanding of the case. Jeanne discovers online the video image reconstructed by an AI of the young Emma Vivian who explains what happened to her. However, her story contains an element that only her captor could know... or her mother.

series.name: Next Level Baker
series.overview: Talented bakers compete through three challenging rounds, crafting spectacular seasonal treats. Only one will emerge victorious and be crowned the ultimate holiday champion.

series.name: Feride vs. The World
series.overview: Feride vs. The World: This edgy and unique Turkish animated series follows the fiercely independent Feride as she struggles to maintain optimism amid the monotony of life.

series.name: Secrets of the Rivers
series.overview: Where the Yellow, Yangtze, and Lancang Rivers begin as one, dwell the three "Water Ghost" clans, the Ding, Jiang, and Yi, along their banks. What are Water Ghosts? Beings who move through water as they please, masters of geomancy and treasure hunting. Yi Sa, the last of her line, runs an "underwater bank" along the Lancang. During a perilous "Golden Soup" dive, she rescues Zong Hang. Seeking truth and a cure for her own fate, Yi Sa trains him as a Water Ghost. Together with Ding Yu Die of the Ding clan, the trio descends into the primordial "Ancestral Golden Soup."

series.name: Let Me Into Your Heart
series.original_name: ขอเป็นพระเอกในหัวใจพระเอก
series.overview: When a “superstar” who is used to the spotlight must step into the artistic world behind the curtain of a charming “Likay leading actor.”

series.name: Aligned Reverence
series.overview: After a tragic mistake leads to the downfall of her benefactors, orphaned Su Jinyuan returns seeking redemption. Her fate becomes entwined with Xie Yunyuan, the adopted son of the fallen family. Together, they defy betrayal, fight to survive, and ignite a passionate, fate-defying love as they seek justice and reclaim their destiny.

series.name: Civilisations: Rise and Fall
series.overview: Four mighty civilisations - Rome, Egypt, Japan's Samurai and the Aztecs. Their legends remain - now priceless artefacts reveal what led them to fall into the echoes of history.

series.name: Ascendants of the Nine Suns
series.overview: Once betrayed and killed at the peak of his power, Ye Yunfei is reborn into his younger self—the moment his martial veins were first destroyed. With all the memories of his past life, he seizes this second chance to protect his loved ones, outmaneuver rival clans and sects, and rebuild his strength.

series.name: Safehaven
series.overview: Safehaven follows Jenna Frost, a fierce, complicated high school comic book artist who must fight to uncover hidden truths after horrifying visions from her drawings come to life-threatening everyone around her. John Rayburn, the mysterious new school counselor determined to save her, even if it endangers both of their lives, and unearths his own personal demons. Complicating matters is Will, a passionate young man committed to protecting Jenna, who finds herself torn between rejecting his help and her growing feelings for him.

series.name: Perfect Family
series.overview: A Punjabi family appears happy but deals with hidden issues, attending therapy together to address mental health and family bonds while fighting cultural stigma.

series.name: Words + Music
series.overview: Iconic artists share stories about songs pivotal to their careers, followed by all-new performances of those songs either solo or with a band. As the artists' stories unfold, the environment around them transforms to reflect each anecdote and song, creating an intimate yet visually stunning experience.

series.name: The Name Doesn't Matter
series.overview: Yazan, a valet who parks more than just cars, slips into a lie—posing as a rich man’s son. But when Lara pulls into his world, love takes the wheel, steering them on a ride of fading identity and burning passion.

series.name: Fated in the Martial World
series.overview: Bai Feifei returns to the martial world seeking revenge, drawing hero Shen Lang, heiress Zhu Qiqi, and the cunning Wang Lianhua into a deadly clash over a powerful treasure, where love and betrayal blur the lines of loyalty.

series.name: Rendezvous at Yunqiu Mountain
series.overview: When strong-willed heiress Lin Jing and gentle inn employee Su Xiaomeng magically switch lives, they’re thrust into each other’s challenges. Lin Jing uses her sharp instincts to transform the struggling inn, while Su Xiaomeng brings warmth and sincerity to revive the Lvye Group. As their unexpected journeys unfold, both women begin to confront their pasts, open themselves to new possibilities, and discover where their true paths may lead.

series.name: Like a Palette
series.original_name: เจน(จะ)เป็นดาวสินกำ
series.overview: Jane is confused about whether P'Dai's feelings are just kindness or if it's something more special!? We'll have to wait and see just when Jane will realize she's being courted!

series.name: No One Like You
series.overview: Luíza Albuquerque sees her life collapse after her daughter runs away from the altar. Shortly after, in an increasingly stifling relationship, she receives a fatal sentence: she has only one year to live, and no amount of money in the world, which she has accumulated – not always in the best way – will be able to save her. Faced with this revelation, she decides to be happy in the short time she has left, even if it means ruining the lives of her sisters and her own daughter.

series.name: Naruto Shippuden Cuarta Guerra Mundial Shinobi
series.original_name: Naruto Shippuden Cuarta Guerra Mundial Shinobi

series.name: Regai
series.overview: SI Vetri investigates a medical team that is trying to cover up deaths of clinical trial participants by staging them as accidents. Can Vetri put an end to this sinister plot before it's too late?

series.name: Love Begins in the World of If
series.original_name: ifの世界で恋がはじまる
series.overview: After wishing to change his life, a quiet worker awakens in a parallel world where he’s confident—and loved by the colleague he admires.

series.name: The Sycamore Gap Mystery
series.overview: When the beloved 200-year-old Sycamore Gap tree on Hadrian’s Wall is mysteriously felled overnight, public outrage erupts worldwide. This gripping two-part true-crime documentary follows Northumbria Police’s unprecedented investigation, with exclusive access to detectives, witnesses and never-before-seen evidence. As officers untangle a bizarre case with no CCTV and no witnesses, the series explores the cultural impact of the tree’s loss and the global fight for justice in one of the UK’s most unusual environmental crimes.

series.name: Hearts in Play
series.overview: When a mixed doubles event leaves table tennis star Xia Fanxing without a partner, she and her diverse group of classmates must convince transfer student Sheng Yang to join. Together, they navigate friendship, teamwork, and the challenges of youth both on and off the court.

series.name: Blood Brothers
series.overview: After a tragic loss shakes his confidence, Zhu Xiao must solve a high-stakes poisoning case to uncover the truth, heal, and reclaim his sense of purpose.

series.name: The Rise of the Qin Empire
series.overview: After the fall of his homeland and the death of his father in battle, Ying Shuo takes the throne as Qin Wen Gong during a time of crisis. With the court divided, brothers turning against each other, and a doomed romance tangled in national turmoil, he pushes forward with sweeping reforms to transform the struggling western state.

series.name: 5-Star
series.overview: As these athletes chase their dreams under the spotlight, they must learn how to navigate playing in the Big Ten Conference while growing up in a pressure-cooker environment. When every mistake can risk everything and the fall from grace is devastatingly real, this isn't just about competing anymore; it's about fighting for a future where glory is within reach.

series.name: LOVE (X)
series.overview:
This is the a ground-breaking and uplifting dating reality show made in Thailand, where 12 single men and women live together in Koh Samui, cut off from the outside world, pursuing boundless love. Through competitive games, they win dates and survival supplies. In the end, they'll make the final choice about who they want to keep seeing after the show.

"X" stands for the unknown, crossing paths and infinite possibilities—find the "X" of your dreams together!

series.name: Prisoner 951
series.overview: The true story of Nazanin Zaghari-Ratcliffe - imprisoned in Iran and separated from her daughter - and her husband Richard, who fights both the British and Iranian governments to facilitate her release.

series.name: Good Sports with Kevin Hart and Kenan Thompson
series.original_name: Good Sports with Kevin Hart and Kenan Thompson
series.overview: Kevin Hart and Kenan Thompson break down their favorite moments from the NFL, NBA and the wide, weird world of sports with colorful commentary on highlights, sketches, celebrity and athlete interviews.

series.name: Toronto Airport Uncovered
series.overview: Behind-the-scenes look at Toronto Pearson Airport shows how Canada's busiest hub manages millions of passengers and aircraft through snowstorms, tech problems, emergencies, and security issues.

series.name: LuBan Mysteries
series.overview: Master carpenter Li Mudun, famed for his skill with ancient Luban techniques, becomes the prime suspect in a series of eerie, superstition-filled murders. Determined to clear his name, Li teams up with detective Yang Zong and forensic doctor Su Qingyun. With reason and justice, the trio races to stop a new wave of killings and expose the truth behind the so-called “supernatural.”

series.name: Yellow
series.overview: It follows two fugitives who steal a taxi to escape from the police.

series.name: The Rocky Mountain Mortician Murder
series.overview: Explores the murder of Byron Griffy, a respected mortician, who was found dead on his remote ranch, shot execution-style.

series.name: O Natal dos Silva
series.overview: It's the Silva family's first Christmas after Dona Zelina's death. Bel keeps the tradition alive but clashes with her sister as tensions rise. Amid fights and gossip, Luciano plans to reveal he's marrying a woman no one in the family met.

series.name: Gifted
series.overview: Set in the breathtaking city of Edinburgh, a diverse group of young Scottish teens discover they each have unique superpowers, from telekinesis to invisibility and mind reading.

series.name: The Palm Line
series.overview: The troubled journalist Anna Romano investigates the theft of a famous Caravaggio painting trying to uncover the truth about her father's mysterious disappearance. Drawn into the world of art trading, amidst financial intrigue and shady dealings with the mafia, she soon realizes that her family is hiding dangerous secrets.

series.name: Heat
